{"type": "article", "id": 51223, "title": "宜家家具没个性？这个新系列希望创造差异化｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-03-18T23:07:41Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 2629, "name": "HAY"}, {"id": 48527, "name": "Natuzzi Italia"}, {"id": 48528, "name": "Tjep"}, {"id": 302, "name": "宜家"}, {"id": 15672, "name": "Marcel Wanders"}, {"id": 32980, "name": "Dima Loginoff"}, {"id": 17363, "name": "Piet Hein Eek"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 123, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180318224955Qq5KYL0UBhXsv3y7.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} span.s6 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none; color: #657ab7; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #657ab7} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Industriell Collection by Piet Hein Eek &amp; Ikea</h3><p>宜家与荷兰设计师 Piet Hein Eek 合作推出了可量产的 INDUSTRIELL 系列，赞美批量生产下的产品独特性与刻意营造的不完美。这个系列中包含家具和精选家居用品，设计师利用算法等技术，增加了设计、图案和颜色的变化，使产品在批量化生产之下仍然有独特的个性。</p><p>刻意营造的不完美之处为这些产品增添了独特之感。这一系列的选材有木材、金属、玻璃、亚麻、陶瓷、合金与编织纸。</p><p>IKEA of Sweden 创意主管 Karin Gustavsson 说：“我们想要打造一个供人们日常生活中使用、价格也不会太贵的系列。通过大批量生产，并利用技术为产品注入刻意的差异特点，我们可以为大众提供更独特的设计。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225049Qji8W0Zy4lONhEkt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225051e0avNEHIojlF7QOh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.365905\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225052ClPDebrs5mcGBWwR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225202MX7ehT1K98SIyqR5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225203hyLdWxaoEk8eSUNl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.dezeen.com/2018/03/18/ikea-piet-hein-eek-industriell-furniture-design/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dezeen</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Vuurs Stove by Tjep</h3><p>传统的室内炉灶造型大多笨重，阿姆斯特丹设计工作室 Tjep 为荷兰品牌 Vuurs 设计了一款更轻巧更当代风格的解决方案。“ Vuurs 希望能创造可以融入当代背景的炉灶。” Tjep 创始人 Frank Tjepkema 表示。他从传统炉灶的形态入手，然后将其简化为更干净的设计版本。</p><p>一般来说，炉灶由深色固体金属制成，通常为铸铁或钢制，并设有封闭的燃烧箱，木材放置其中。但 Tjep 采用浅色色调，将柔和的灰色和灰白色相结合。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318230115l78m0rniVO9ybuBc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.502961\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225241qnh8YBv6fkpxHjZM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562207\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225241EPlD3WdyHsRUISXY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665398\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225244S7Pmbg5uqhQ6eVTL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.460660\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Siren Light by Dima Loginoff </h3><p>俄罗斯设计师 Dima Loginoff 为捷克照明品牌 Preciosa 设计了一款钟形曲线的吊灯 Siren，它包括三个具有不同尺寸和透明度的外壳，它们相互叠放在一起。</p><p>Siren 吊灯由手工垂直的玻璃制成，表面做了磨砂处理，意在散发出更柔和的光线。两端各有一个玻璃球体，你可以将其看作是装饰元素。Siren 是 Preciosa Solitaires 系列的一部分，更加当代简约的形式意在与该品牌 1724 年创立以来生产的华丽吊灯形成鲜明对比。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225428edXOCbZ62nQJBYAo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706430\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225428dsb53QeNgizxhPHG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.648900\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225429lkaYMSvBRIXsz128.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225430WtaPDb8cJgXjmSIN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Thomas Heatherwick, Bethan Laura Wood and more nominate emerging designers for Aram Gallery exhibition</h3><p>包括 Thomas Heatherwick，  Ineke Hans，  Jasper Morrison 和  Bethan Laura Wood 在内的 15 位设计师为伦敦 Aram 画廊的新展览 Designers Select Designers 量身而做了各种作品，这是为纪念画廊成立 15 周年举办的一次展览，意在推广当代设计。</p><p>Thomas Heatherwick 设计的扭曲橱柜，由两个对称的弧形面板组成。Kayser 的项目 Solar Sinister的特色是使用3D打印机制成的碗。荷兰设计师 Ineke Hans 是可叠放的凳子，可也做儿童的边桌或踏脚凳。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225459UX1Ah5FPkO8oWiGQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562793\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225501lTiWq138XepKMy42.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.802876\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225501B3hVvQ681YquATJW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225503mZeqO35xVglMQzL1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225503yrgV8pJ7o4kYfNXs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.994501\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225505AGtWrZy6mD9XHvSw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.334602\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225505RNaSPdtV8i1sGcCp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.501692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225505HIWeZlh8msF2pciw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225509Phd0Tk7O8nzXwlQ3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500423\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>The Cozy Furrow Sofa by Marcel Wanders for Natuzzi Italia</h3><p>2018 年对于意大利品牌 Natuzzi Italia 来说是个新的开始，Pasquale Junior Natuzzi 开始掌管家族企业，将其转型为一个生活品牌。</p><p>荷兰设计师 Marcel Wanders 为其设计的新款沙发 Furrow，就是其转型后亮相的第一个作品。它的材质看起来像是老式棒球手套的那种柔软光滑的感觉。弯曲的沙发造型，灵感源自普利亚的自然美景，就像是那里温厚的棕色土壤。其圆润的背部和两侧造型，意在让用户联想到茧，而其红棕色皮革和骑马订缝合的样式，则为用户提供了量身定制的舒适感。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225540zlpQoeg6Z9YR4j2A.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.752344\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225540CLqHed6ylWDMT7QO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225540dLnIzsK8P1BO6GUl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.903906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225541NGKVzaR4cwCpFtA5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.638281\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/furrow-sofa-by-marcel-wanders-for-natuzzi-italia/natuzzi-furrow-sofa-marcel-wanders-4/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Uchiwa by Nipa for HAY</h3><p>Uchiwa是一个宽扶手椅，灵感来源于日本传统手扇打开的形状。Uchiwa的硬塑料壳充满了大量的暄软内充，舒适宜人。</p><p>它既会带给你熟悉感也会带给你新鲜感，扶手椅有两个版本：一个是能让你全身放松的暄软版和另一个是让你直背挺胸的模塑泡沫版。可直接坐于独特设计的座壳或铺上软垫，座椅腿是天然色或染色橡木。椅子有一个附带的凳脚，使你的双脚可以舒适的自然伸展。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803182256261G0exVQsa8cPLpkt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803182256261Fqfu9abQzig6UZE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201803182256266UpkwyB8Wnh13FEK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.575217\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180318225632t8HYe9VFIU7aBqih.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div>"}